WEBVTT

00:00:00.641 --> 00:00:02.995
Želim vam ispričati priču

00:00:02.995 --> 00:00:06.171
koja povezuje slavan incident s privatnošću

00:00:06.171 --> 00:00:08.940
Adama i Eve,

00:00:08.940 --> 00:00:12.386
te izuzetno pomicanje granica

00:00:12.386 --> 00:00:15.072
između javnog i privatnog koje se dogodilo

00:00:15.072 --> 00:00:16.842
u zadnjih 10 godina.

00:00:16.842 --> 00:00:18.140
Znate za taj incident.

00:00:18.140 --> 00:00:21.470
Jednoga dana u Edenskom vrtu, Adam i Eva

00:00:21.470 --> 00:00:23.313
shvate da su goli.

00:00:23.313 --> 00:00:24.813
Izbezume se.

00:00:24.813 --> 00:00:27.570
I ostalo je povijest.

00:00:27.570 --> 00:00:29.758
Danas, Adam i Eva

00:00:29.758 --> 00:00:32.119
bi vjerojatno postupili drukčije.